quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  36,55,ahal jannat is roz aish wa nishaat ke mashghelay mein hon ge
  36,56,woh bhi aur un ki biwiyan bhi saayon mein takhton par takiye lagaye baithy hon ge
  36,57,wahan un ke liye meway aur jo chahain ge ( mojood hoga )
  36,58,perwar-digaar meharban ki taraf se salam ( kaha jaye ga )
  36,59,aur gunahgaro! aaj allag ho jao
  36,60,ae aadam ki aulaad hum ne tum se keh nahi diya tha ke shetan ko nah poojna woh tumhara khula dushman hai
  36,61,aur yeh ke meri hi ibadat karna. yahi seedha rasta hai
  36,62,aur is ne tum mein se bohat si khalqat ko gumraah kardiya tha. tokiya tum samajte nahi they ?
  36,63,yahi woh jahannum hai jis ki tumhe khabar di jati hai
  36,64,( so ) jo tum kufar karte rahay ho is ke badlay aaj is mein daakhil hojao
  36,65,aaj hum un ke monhon par mohar laga den ge aur jo kuch yeh karte rahay they un ke haath hum se bayan kar dein ge aur un ke paon ( is ki ) gawahi den ge
  36,66,aur agar hum chahain to un ki aankhon ko mita kar ( andha kar ) den. phir yeh raste ko dorhin to kahan dekh saken ge
  36,67,aur agar hum chahain to un ki jagah par un ki soorten badal den phir wahan se nah agay ja sakain aur nah ( peechay ) lout saken
  36,68,aur jis ko hum barri Umar dete hain to usay khalqat mein ondha kardete hain tokiya yeh samajte nahi ?
  36,69,aur hum ne un ( paighambar ) ko shair goi nahi sikhayi aur nah woh un ko Shayaan hai. yeh to mehez nasiyaat aur saaf saaf quran ( pur az hikmat ) hai
  36,70,taakay is shakhs ko jo zindah ho hadaayat ka rasta dukhaay aur kafiroon par baat poori hojaye
